title: Fight Club
alt: I'm not saying it's all bad, but that movie has not aged as well as my teenage self in 2000 was confident it would.
transcript:
Friend: But Fight Club isn't really about fighting. It's about the way society—
Cueball: Nope, don't wanna hear it.
Friend: But it says consumers are—
Cueball: This conversation is over.The first rule of talking to me about movies is do NOT talk about Fight Club.
